column5: Has the ownership of onaman river resort changed in the last year or two?
Same Owners were there as of September 2018.
That's a start. What I had heard was the ownership changes some time between June 2017 and June 2018
I've confirmed my dates for 2019, with Robert, last December.He didn't mention any changes this coming year.Looking forward to at least another week at Onaman this year, our 8th year at this camp.
